    "10": {
      "content": "> ****About this dashboard:****\n> Built by **Oludolapo Lawrence** as part of a Dynatrace Grail observability implementation.\n> All DQL queries were authored and validated against live Grail span, log and entity data.\n> This dashboard monitors the `frontend` service — covering throughput, latency, database span analysis and log error patterns.\n> Inspired by a real production incident involving Oracle DB connection pool exhaustion that impacted payment card transactions.\n>\n> **Stack:** Dynatrace SaaS · Grail · DQL · Gen3 dashboards\n> **GitHub:** [github.com/oludevops/dynatrace-grail-observability](https://github.com/oludevops/dynatrace-grail-observability)\n**Environment:** Dynatrace Sandbox/playground",
      "type": "markdown"
